<title>USA: Image Entertainment in DVD agreement.</title>
<headline>Image Entertainment in DVD agreement.</headline>
<dateline>CHATSWORTH, Calif 1997-07-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Image Entertainment Inc reached an agreement to bring twelve of Metromedia Entertainment Group Home Video's major titles to the new digital video disc format (DVD) pursuant to an exclusive license agreement.</p>
<p>Under the agreement, Image market, sell and distribute  DVD titles in both the U.S. and Canada.</p>
